30:18.000Z","msg":"推唔到都推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【警世良言】中共劇本係想抹黑「香港人打砸搶燒」，然後種族滅絕！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1623758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1623758</a><br />\n<br />\n大家要冷靜, 理性分析, 我地唔可以變成中共口中既暴徒"},{"pid":"2e9514f416279c55b65a97893554b8f2b71c477d","tid":1630991,"uid":42550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:30:40.000Z","msg":"己經講左十九幾萬次<br />\n<br />\n係咪未見過狗做鬼？<br />\n<br />\n你不如諗下點樣樣阻止狗做鬼好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795a648c4d2d5d0efe001b52bcbcfa621fa0fc00","tid":1630991,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:32:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"10c11cb9ef81421f53d810e6d90db4c0298b7f02","tid":1630991,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:32:18.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}